Newest HCM Whitepapers
          




10 More Ways to Wow Your New Hire
It’s never too early to focus on engagement for your workforce. These best practices can help you harness the needed tools and plan ahead to craft an outstanding employee experience for your hires.


HR's Secret Weapon: The Power of Big Data
Big Data is more than a buzzword. Rich, accurate data is constantly being amassed from more sources at a faster rate than ever before. In fact, 90% of all data ever collected has been collected in the last two years. Business intelligence is evolving to provide.


Business Performance Toolkit for Manufacturing
Stay on top of new breakthroughs and adapt rapidly, while handling day-to-day challenges like overtime calculations, union compliance, managing multiple subsidiaries, a large variety of job codes, and more. 


Business Performance Toolkit for Retail
Learn what has led many leaders in the retail industry to adopt unified, comprehensive human capital management (HCM) for everything from payroll processing to advanced business analytics.


Business Performance Toolkit for Hospitality
Discover how leading hotels and tourist destinations have achieved outstanding business results with better people management.


