		Exploring Careers at Ultimate Software























































LANGUAGE






Ultimate Software














CAREERS


OUR PEOPLE


HIRING


WELCOMING


INSPIRING


DEVELOPING


REWARDING




 










UltiCareers
People first.

What We Believe: People come first in our work & personal lives.
At Ultimate Software, we believe that people are the most important ingredient of any business. It is the people who tell the true story of what that business stands for—and it is the people who ultimately determine what can be achieved. That is why creating a culture based on trust, respect, and inclusion is a high priority for us. We encourage and trust our people to always reach higher, learn more, and live up to their potential, delivering our customers the best global people management solutions possible.
VIEW OPEN POSITIONS


VIEW OPEN POSITIONS






GREAT PLACE TO WORK
If you’re talented, energetic, and committed to delivering quality human capital management (HCM) software and services, you'll find that Ultimate Software is the perfect place to work. You’ll grow professionally and share your knowledge and experience with coworkers.
Your work will be challenging and your performance will be recognized and rewarded. You’ll be part of a team of dedicated professionals applying your talents to achieving shared goals and delivering results. We're focused on providing the best end-to-end strategic human resources, payroll, and talent management solutions available—and we need the best employees in the industry to continue to succeed.
OUR CULTURE
There are many things that Ultimate Software does to show its employees they’re valued—on-site massage service, dry-cleaning service, indoor basketball court, exercise and salsa classes, Weight Watchers group, birthday celebrations, inter-departmental bowling contests, periodic breakfast, lunch, and ice cream treats, departmental reward trips/programs, and so much more!
Ultimate Software is committed to equal employment opportunity and does not discriminate with regard to the terms or conditions of employment on race, color, sex, sexual orientation, gender identity, gender expression, age, religion, national origin, military service, or disability (provided employee is physically/mentally able to perform the regular duties of his/her job). 
We have been named the #1 Workplace for Hispanics and Latinos by FORTUNE, and as one of the Best Workplaces for African-Americans. As of August 2016, Hispanics and African-Americans comprise 30 percent of our overall employee population, compared with about 10 percent at four of the largest FORTUNE 500 technology companies. Moreover, 20 percent are members of Ultimate’s leadership team (manager or above), compared with an average of about six percent at four of the largest FORTUNE 500 companies in tech. 
COMMUNITIES OF INTEREST 
Military Veterans at Ultimate (UltiVets) 
UltiVets is a community of interest for military veterans at Ultimate, their friends and families, and for fellow UltiPeeps to express their appreciation for the service of our nation’s veterans. Ultimate proudly hires veterans from every military branch to contribute in all areas of the organization. We are 100 UltiVets strong and growing! Their service to our country gives us an incredible sense of pride, and the leadership and expertise our UltiVets hold in their respective fields helps make Ultimate stronger.
PRIDE US 
Ultimate’s first Community of Interest, PRIDE US, was founded in May of 2014 for lesbian, gay, bisexual, transgender, queer/questioning,     intersex and ally (LGBTQIA) team members. Our mission is for our LGBTQIA UltiPeeps to feel safe, welcome, and comfortable bringing their whole selves to work while volunteering to help make the world a better place for everyone. The PRIDE US community of interest is a great resource of information as well as support to anyone who is having difficulty coming out, are parents, family members of LGBTQI and need someone to talk to or just want to make a difference in creating equality for everyone and support fellow UltiPeeps.
Women in Leadership 
Our second Community of Interest is for UltiWomen at all levels of the organization. The Women in Leadership community is dedicated to helping women achieve their maximum potential and allows them to discuss their goals, ask questions, and collaborate with one another on how they can positively impact future female leaders at work, at school, and in the community. In 2016, Ultimate was named one of FORTUNE’s Best Workplaces for Women. As of August 2016, UltiWomen comprise 49 percent of our total workforce, and 42 percent hold leadership positions (manager or above) at Ultimate.

Learn more about Ultimate Software’s EEO Policy.
Learn more about Ultimate Software's External Recruiting Policy.
