		Investor Relations: Committed to Providing Shareholders with a Top People Management Solution

























































LANGUAGE






Ultimate Software








Investor Relations







Ultimate Software (Nasdaq: ULTI) is a leading cloud provider of comprehensive human capital management (HCM) solutions. Our award-winning, cloud-delivered human resources, payroll, and talent management transformed our business from primarily a license model to a subscription model for a higher percentage of recurring revenues. UltiPro is Ultimate Software's flagship SaaS solution that allows organizations to access greater people management functionality in the cloud.  

Founded in 1990 and headquartered in Weston, Florida, Ultimate is committed to sustaining a culture of mutual respect and ethical behavior. Our more than 3,800 employees live their professional lives by our 'people first' philosophy that leads us to always do what's best for our customers, our shareholders, our employees, and our community.

Shareholders, potential investors, and the investment community can learn more about Ultimate Software's financial performance by reading our financial statements, annual reports, and policies on corporate governance provided within this section of the website.



