On-Demand HCM Webcast
The Power of Perception: Insight to Enhance the Employee Experience
Do you know what your people really think about work?



UltiPro Perception™ reveals what your people care about the most so you can make positive changes in your workplace. 


A modern take on the employee survey, this innovative new UltiPro solution blends human technology with the human experience to measure what your people say and think about their work environment, culture, and leadership.

We’ll share how Perception lets you:

Gather feedback through mobile-friendly, conversational surveys.
Interpret open-ended questions like what’s on your mind? to gain valuable insight.
Analyze and share interactive reports in seconds.
Create dashboards that promote action.


When you’re tuned into the voice of your employees, it’s easy to know the right steps to enhance your peoples’ experience at work. 
Fill out the short form to register for this on-demand one-hour webcast. 

Speakers

Erik Darby, Sr. Director in Strategic Accounts & Alliances, Ultimate Software
Suhail Halai, Sr. Manager Strategic Accounts, Ultimate Software












